<div class="notes-answer">
  <h3>How do I send an email to my entire family?</h3>
  <ol>
    <li>
      In the text box labeled "To:" type in the email addresses of
      each of your family members, separating each email address by a comma.
    </li>
    
    <li>Compose the rest of the email as you would normally compose any other email.</li>
    
    <li>
      Send the email.  Each of the email addresses listed in the "To:" text box will
      receive a copy of the email.
    </li>
  </ol>
</div>
